stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB

    [*] --> q_init
    q_init --> q_check_type : isinstance(tx, LegacyTransaction)
    q_check_type --> q_encode_legacy : tx is LegacyTransaction
    q_check_type --> q_hash_bytes : tx is Bytes
    q_encode_legacy --> q_hash_legacy : encoded = rlp.encode(tx)
    q_hash_legacy --> q_final : return keccak256(encoded)
    q_hash_bytes --> q_final : return keccak256(tx)
    q_final --> [*]

    note right of q_check_type
        INV-001: Input must be LegacyTransaction or Bytes
        INV-002: Legacy txs are RLP-encoded before hashing
        INV-003: Typed txs hashed as-is (include type prefix)
    end note
